      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC6a3dfcd024f2100583a5b051d7198fd2"></a>Reassembly of the oil pump
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10816"> </a>Check that the key (8) and the O-Rings (6) are present on the pump.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e10818"> </a>Fit the pump drive gear (7) on to the oil pump and secure it by installing the circlip (6) in its groove.
         </div>
      </div>
